Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.00,0:02:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(贊斯巴爾之追擊！)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.34,0:02:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帝姆艦隊在21時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.95,0:02:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在賈布羅準備出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.85,0:02:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以白色基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.75,0:02:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要在出發前二個小時\N先離開這裡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.32,0:02:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要提早二個小時出發？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.19,0:02:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯！呀\N以剛完成的二艘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.76,0:02:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加上三艘修理的一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.93,0:02:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們今次讓帝姆艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直前去月神二號基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.63,0:02:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但母艦則以反方向\N的軌道前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.73,0:02:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後去攻擊目標...\N所羅門基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.44,0:02:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.24,0:02:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色基地將在\N今日19時去太空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.61,0:02:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊少尉，請保重身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.55,0:02:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多謝妳，將軍\N我會了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.88,0:02:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們放心吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.05,0:02:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當所羅門被攻佔後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.45,0:02:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吉翁軍便沒有軍力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.99,0:02:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時便會向我們\N提出和談要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.22,0:02:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這樣\N戰爭便很快結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.26,0:02:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到那時候\N就讓我來為妳作媒人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.10,0:03:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀...我記得\N妳有個未婚夫呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.40,0:03:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.57,0:03:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.81,0:03:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這門親事是長輩們訂的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.78,0:03:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他現在那裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.98,0:03:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了逃避戰爭\N已去了衛星六號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.58,0:03:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們倆人從未見過面的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.62,0:03:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們回來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色基地準備\N在1小時後出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.26,0:03:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出發前\N大家先作好準備！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.33,0:03:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉！誰是白色基地\N的負責人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.27,0:03:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找他有什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.80,0:03:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我問他在那裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.20,0:03:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特，有人找你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.87,0:03:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是史列加中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.64,0:03:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後起便調派來母艦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.55,0:03:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊，真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.05,0:03:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？...是真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.28,0:03:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的運氣確不錯呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.65,0:03:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以和這麼美的小姐\N一起工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.56,0:03:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請多多指教，我叫米萊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.42,0:03:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請多多指教！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.70,0:04:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請多多指教！這位小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.43,0:04:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫雪拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.67,0:04:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看妳愁眉不展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.24,0:04:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎為男人的事\N而煩惱呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.91,0:04:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的睡房在那裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.81,0:04:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我們想\N邁向成功的第一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.98,0:04:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關鍵是各位勇敢的行動上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.45,0:04:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我們地球聯邦軍\N戰勝的那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.58,0:04:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到勝利的一刻時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.45,0:04:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位一定會被國民所讚頌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.25,0:04:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為偉大的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在此，我預祝各位\N能夠順利成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.92,0:04:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看他長得那麼高大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.49,0:04:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像已死去的\N良哥哥呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.33,0:04:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過他會一樣的仁慈嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.60,0:04:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看他不像是這種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.23,0:04:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們出發了\N快回自己崗位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.10,0:04:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解除所有固定制\N白色基地出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.39,0:05:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上空一切正常，打開大門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.23,0:05:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很美呢！         是啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.44,0:05:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在有空閒人的\N可以看看左舷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.87,0:05:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一大群紅鶴飛過呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可不可以\N用錄影機拍下來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.24,0:05:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的，我批准吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.65,0:06:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木馬號到底去了那裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.45,0:06:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像剛從賈布羅出發了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.22,0:06:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！我們要快了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.89,0:06:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,30分鐘後\N便進入作戰距離了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.06,0:06:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勞煩你\N希將軍不高興嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.40,0:06:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.97,0:06:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連我一樣也有這種想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.67,0:06:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這艘贊斯巴爾\N沒有新型的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.24,0:06:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢格羅配備的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.74,0:07:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就別去追木馬號了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.21,0:07:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞上校\N那個畢格羅要去看嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.88,0:07:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔，帶我去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.28,0:07:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要做好準備！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.65,0:07:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用它來對付普通的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.65,0:07:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論速度和戰鬥力方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.89,0:07:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是高出好幾倍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.32,0:07:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本不是它的對手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.66,0:07:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但只有一個是不夠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.29,0:07:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀！還有兩個多姆\N在試驗附助器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.73,0:07:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多姆？陸戰用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.66,0:07:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！基本上\N加上特別的構造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.67,0:07:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是改良型嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.90,0:07:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事實上\N和以前的相比較好用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.14,0:07:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提高警覺！快作攻擊了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.24,0:07:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去集合駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.98,0:07:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道木馬號的位置後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.85,0:07:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便開始進攻！         是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.69,0:07:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在後面追來的\N好像是贊斯巴爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果再這樣下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.42,0:07:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要20分鐘\N便可追上來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.56,0:07:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在應該怎辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.69,0:07:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好極！不用改變航導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.39,0:07:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在E3點開始加速前進\N是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.63,0:08:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照這樣看\N母艦便是在航向月球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.97,0:08:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的目的就是這樣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.64,0:08:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞會來的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.40,0:08:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一定會來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.67,0:08:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，妳還在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.71,0:08:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連檢查G戰機\N的時間也沒有了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.88,0:08:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.11,0:08:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳怎知道一定是夏亞呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.92,0:08:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...因為母艦\N好像和他有點緣份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.22,0:08:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我...      妳怕他嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.42,0:08:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡有人不怕他嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.33,0:08:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,認為如何？米萊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.80,0:08:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她一定很疲倦了！\N否則不會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.47,0:08:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也相信是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.67,0:08:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木馬號突然增加速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.21,0:08:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目標好像是向著月球呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.51,0:08:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月球？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.01,0:08:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想去希莉亞將軍\N的古拉拿達？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.91,0:08:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會的\N而且還上當呢！被騙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.52,0:08:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木馬是餌，在賈布羅內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.42,0:08:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在一定還有別的艦隊\N正在出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.02,0:08:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然這樣\N我們回航去攻擊他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.29,0:09:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你傻了嗎？如果我們回航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.73,0:09:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木馬就會向我們攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.86,0:09:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且只有利用這個機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.93,0:09:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打一場硬仗了！      是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.20,0:09:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在查知是贊斯巴爾了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.54,0:09:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡可能放大鏡頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.97,0:09:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有多久才可攻擊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.34,0:09:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一會！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.74,0:09:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2分20秒後\N便有直接攻擊過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.65,0:09:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.88,0:09:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,G戰機，準備出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.95,0:09:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼坦克，等候命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.32,0:09:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開各炮門\N打開雷射炮門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.96,0:09:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何官，吩咐\N畢格羅準備出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.20,0:09:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.17,0:09:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有，兩個多姆\N亦要出戰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.40,0:09:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何官上尉\N我現在出發了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.98,0:09:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,G翔戰機，G戰鬥機\N準備出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.22,0:10:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞到母艦後面\N準備迎擊敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.89,0:10:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看妳現在愁眉不展\N似乎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.19,0:10:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你只為何薩比家報復\N才這樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.40,0:10:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我根本就不贊成\N你的做法...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.40,0:10:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,G翔戰機出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.71,0:10:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,G戰機EG型出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.88,0:10:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，請妳離我遠些吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.02,0:10:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假如在這裡遇上攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.62,0:10:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩架也有可能被擊中的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.09,0:10:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.83,0:10:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳小心一點！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.33,0:10:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假如速度太高\N會被引力吸過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要保持\N適當的速度才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.17,0:10:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你\N我會小心的！來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.54,0:10:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後面的火箭炮\N快發射掩護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.08,0:10:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.95,0:11:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，看我的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.42,0:11:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很快呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.09,0:11:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們避不過\N畢格羅的高速的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.33,0:11:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,威力很強\N但機動力很差呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.70,0:11:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用雷射炮攻擊吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.87,0:11:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道，哥哥在裡面嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.88,0:11:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行了，雪拉，快上昇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.92,0:11:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有三台敵方MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.82,0:11:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要鋼加農出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.86,0:11:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，叫凱的\N鋼加農出動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.69,0:11:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史列加中尉在那裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.40,0:11:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,噢，有什麼事？\N我在控制室下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.67,0:11:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有什麼專長？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.50,0:11:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的專長大概是\N戰鬥機也行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.30,0:11:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然如此\N請你去控制主炮吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.07,0:12:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我有條件的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.91,0:12:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,條件？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.31,0:12:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將白色基地\N開去敵人那邊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.31,0:12:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在駛過去\N應該沒問題的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.35,0:12:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這豈不是被敵人追上來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.52,0:12:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話我不做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.89,0:12:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我沒自信會打中的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.10,0:12:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽住\N再攻擊15秒便停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.44,0:12:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果再攻擊的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.21,0:12:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可能連自己人\N也會殃及的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.09,0:12:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真危險...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.89,0:12:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去後面\N用機槍打倒他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.76,0:12:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一於去打，打倒敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.09,0:12:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這艘木馬愈來愈成熟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.90,0:13:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是換了艦長嗎？不過...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.67,0:13:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該不會是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,普通的市民\N居然演變成軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.14,0:13:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還可在戰艦上作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.71,0:13:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿爾黛西亞...阿爾黛西亞...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.48,0:13:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那時候見到阿爾黛西亞妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.45,0:13:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是穿著軍服的\N我不相信...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.92,0:13:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿爾黛西亞最恨就是戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.15,0:13:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她沒可能去當軍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.25,0:13:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她根本不會\N在木馬上作戰的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.66,0:13:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！再過3秒\N就停止用炮攻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.46,0:13:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞄準才發射啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.10,0:13:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起！我不是有意的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.87,0:13:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？布萊特！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.10,0:13:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中尉，恕我不客氣說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.61,0:13:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然你年紀比我大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.28,0:13:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但指揮權仍然\N是在我身上的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.74,0:13:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點我明白的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.45,0:13:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道就好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.28,0:13:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才要求你\N將母艦回航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.75,0:13:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待我主炮容易發揮作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.65,0:13:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在仍未可以\N再等一會吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.79,0:14:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何不能上昇的？\N怎樣好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.66,0:14:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火箭炮，發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.80,0:14:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發射火箭不是這樣的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轉過去了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.32,0:14:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看著吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.92,0:14:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也很拚命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.26,0:14:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛過頭很易丟下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.82,0:14:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他居然一點也不怕\N好膽色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.00,0:14:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出現一架好像是機動堡壘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.54,0:14:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼加農準備\N請快出動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.07,0:14:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱，你在做甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.91,0:14:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了，剛有問題？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.88,0:14:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在彈射器可以了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.55,0:14:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去幫助掩護雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.98,0:14:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，我現在去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.45,0:15:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將鋼坦克固定在出口處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.89,0:15:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要用作炮台的，知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.23,0:15:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，我會告訴准人的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.93,0:15:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色基地\N180度回轉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.24,0:15:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真行，布拉度中尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.67,0:15:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確有頭腦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.57,0:15:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你去主炮射擊位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.91,0:15:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊小姐\N母艦交給妳駕駛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.68,0:15:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.36,0:15:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們在那裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.86,0:15:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不可一直在這裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.53,0:15:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真佩服...阿姆羅和雪拉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.88,0:15:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去是不行的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.88,0:16:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我己佔了壓倒勝優勢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.21,0:16:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收拾你只是時間的問題！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.72,0:16:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉...是凱！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.05,0:16:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁有他掩護\N我要變成鋼彈作戰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.76,0:16:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何\N先要減低速度...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.23,0:16:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是被擊中\N便兇多吉少了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.56,0:16:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過若太慢又危險！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.67,0:16:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！可以進行連接了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.75,0:16:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，妳沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.68,0:16:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，你要快點啊！\N是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，你認為那個駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.22,0:16:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會是什麼人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.19,0:16:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？怎會問起這個的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.53,0:16:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.56,0:16:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，多姆來了！\N小心點！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.73,0:16:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！   我沒事\N我會想辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.61,0:17:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,G戰機已連接妥當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.62,0:17:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士的位置\N已降低了高度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.95,0:17:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以進行攻擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家注意，準備防禦工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.66,0:17:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在沒辦法\N不用火箭炮自衛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.46,0:17:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家準備攻擊\N要一面閃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.06,0:17:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一面攻擊，要瞄準呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.70,0:17:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有30秒進入有效射程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底木馬號\N和贊斯巴爾的射程距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.97,0:17:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰會佔優勢呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.37,0:17:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信只有神才知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.28,0:17:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿爾黛西亞\N妳會在木馬號內嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.98,0:17:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只得3分鐘時間閃避\N知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.99,0:17:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有20秒進入射程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.99,0:17:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有20秒就展開攻擊\N唔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.86,0:17:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,15秒...各單位準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.03,0:18:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知這艘母艦\N主炮的威力如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.87,0:18:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們看著吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.20,0:18:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,3，2...1...      好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.77,0:18:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們攻擊了！\N還擊！   別急！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.41,0:18:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吩咐他們別開炮\N要再近一點！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.65,0:18:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火箭炮要連續發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.89,0:18:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！可以發炮了！發炮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.07,0:18:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們即管看著\N我要打沉你們！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.04,0:18:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！就當我們想衝過去\N衝過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.27,0:18:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.88,0:18:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這比起周圍閃避\N更加安全！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.98,0:18:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你即管相信我吧！   是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.41,0:18:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贊斯巴爾完全不閃避\N繼續衝過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.35,0:18:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？米萊，快回右駛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.65,0:19:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞，這種打法\N一定是夏亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.39,0:19:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉說得沒錯\N一定是夏亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.70,0:19:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木馬號已經怕了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.37,0:19:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開炮時先要瞄準才好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.44,0:19:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豈有此理！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.22,0:19:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中彈了！      滋味如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.78,0:19:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰叫你們先來攻擊母艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.69,0:19:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦尾火箭炮，快發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.18,0:19:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還未呢...我不怕的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.75,0:20:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有一台多姆，鋼彈呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.76,0:20:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.63,0:20:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果太快，就會失准了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.00,0:20:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要你知道畢格羅的利害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.11,0:20:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下面好像有物件掛住！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.21,0:20:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是鋼彈？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.95,0:20:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...不會的\N憑現時的速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.88,0:20:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他應該已經暈了才對！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.97,0:20:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.68,0:21:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？\N那駕駛員怎會沒事的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.72,0:21:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其它的MS和贊斯巴爾呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.53,0:21:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一個多姆已撤退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.86,0:21:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，你沒事吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.30,0:21:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何官竟然被他消滅了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.90,0:21:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞上校\N請你准許我出擊吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.71,0:21:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別急，他們現在\N已是網中魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.94,0:21:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有很多機會的！   是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.35,0:21:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吩咐他們\N修理被破壞的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.88,0:21:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，為什麼\N妳會這樣說？   咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.92,0:21:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳剛才不是有問我\N駕駛員是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.49,0:21:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看他好像很利害似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.40,0:21:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才這樣問而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.16,0:21:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.90,0:21:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在第一階段總算成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.00,0:21:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯！我們已瞄準\N贊斯巴爾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.17,0:22:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史列加中尉，你真行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.41,0:22:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有你才可擊中對方的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.84,0:22:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算得什麼呢！\N只是碰幸運氣而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.65,0:22:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實你們也很能幹呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.71,0:22:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的，辛苦大家了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.88,0:22:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次敵人速度\N實在太快了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.19,0:22:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯！\N我當時還真害怕！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.19,0:22:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和贊斯巴爾擦身而過呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.96,0:22:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一定是夏亞\N的作戰方法！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.26,0:22:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞？         唔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.19,0:22:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種戰法其它人\N一定不夠膽用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.26,0:22:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真佩服妳呢\N雪拉小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.07,0:22:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳擊落了一架MS\N真能幹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.00,0:22:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這麼說...\N我也是好運而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.01,0:22:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳太謙虛了\N我一看就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.54,0:22:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳的技術是一流的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.04,0:22:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是了，我現在想先洗個澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.65,0:22:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只餘5分鐘時間啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.32,0:22:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人很快會回頭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.88,0:22:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了\N米萊小姐妳去不去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.95,0:22:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你自己去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.55,0:22:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！是！我們去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.62,0:22:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我們去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.89,0:22:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又去！

